  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="AN189.1-kilavi">makaṭpōkkiya cevili colliyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">What the foster mother said who had let [her] daughter go.</p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AN189.1">
        <l>pacumpaḻap palaviṉ kāṉam vempi</l>
        <l>vicumpukaṇ ṇaḻiya vēṉi ṉīṭik</l>
        <l>kayaṅka ṇaṟṟa kallōṅku vaippi</l>
        <l>ṉāṟuyir maṭappiṭi taḻīi vēṟunāṭṭu</l>
        <l>viḻavuppaṭar maḷḷariṉ muḻaveṭut tuyarik</l>
        <l>kaḷiṟatarp paṭutta kalluyar kavāaṉ</l>
        <l>vevvarai yattañ cuṭṭip paiyeṉap</l>
        <l>payalaiyam piṇaiyal vārnta kavarvuṟat</l>
        <l>titalai yalkuṟ kuṟumaka ḷavaṉoṭu</l>
        <l>ceṉṟupiṟa <supplied>ḷā</supplied>kiya vaḷavai yeṉṟum</l>
        <l><supplied>pa</supplied>ṭarmali yevvamoṭu mātiran tuḻaii</l>
        <l>maṉaimaruṇ ṭirunta veṉṉiṉu naṉaimakiḻ</l>
        <l>naṉṉa rāḷar kūṭuko ḷiṉṉiyan</l>
        <l>tērūr teruviṟ ṟatumpu</l>
        <l>mūriḻan taṉṟutaṉ vīḻvuṟu poruḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>As the forest of jack trees with green fruit is hot, (1)</l>
        <l>summer extending so that the area of the sky is deserted [by clouds], (2)</l>
        <l>in the region high with stones where the area of ponds has disappeared, (3)</l>
        <l>on the slope high with stones on which the elephant bull has made a road, (6)</l>
        <l>raising high [its] drum [voice], like warriors setting out for a festival (5)</l>
        <l>in other lands, embracing [its] youthful cow with fragrant breath, (4)</l>
        <l>in as much as [my] little girl, [her] hips with beauty spots,</l>
        <l>so that [we] with [our] pale wreath feel overflowing sorrow,</l>
        <l>softly, pointing to the road through the hot mountains,</l>
        <l>has gone with him [and thus] has become another, (7-10c)</l>
        <l>even more than me who was in confusion, [back] in the house (12a-c)</l>
        <l>after having searched the great directions with trouble abounding in affliction, (11)</l>
        <l>[this] village, (15a)</l>
        <l>where in the street crawling with chariots resound (14)</l>
        <l>in unison the sweet instruments of good men [intoxicated] with fresh toddy (12df.)</l>
        <l rend="indent5">has lost a wealth it cherishes. (15)</l>
      </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
